content: Had to deal with a bug in Xander's chatbot module where he was giving out financial advice. Fixed it by refining his training data to stay within his scope. Also, got an email from my firm - they're interested in my DeFi project. Meeting next week to discuss potential team lead role.

Xander's urban exploration feature is live! We mapped out a weekend trip to Brooklyn's lesser-known spots, blending in sustainability themes. My talk at the meetup went well, got some offers to collaborate on AI projects. And, the firm approved my DeFi project, I'm now leading a small team.
